# Portfolio Controller

This project is a Chrome Manifest V3 extension that lets users customize the display order of accounts on the Fidelity portfolio page.

## Purpose

- Detect account rows from the Fidelity portfolio account selector.
- Let the user reorder detected accounts from the extension popup.
- Save the preferred order with `chrome.storage.sync`.
- Reapply the saved order on Fidelity pages while leaving new or unmatched accounts visible after ordered accounts.
